flavor_text_entries.gold:
Its paws conceal
sharp claws. If
attacked, it sud­ denly extends the
claws and startles
its enemy.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
Vicious in nature,
it drives PIDGEY
from their nests and feasts on the
eggs that are left
behind.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
This cunning
POKéMON hides
under the cover of darkness,
waiting to attack
its prey.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
SNEASEL scales trees by punching its
hooked claws into the bark.
This POKéMON seeks out unguarded nests and steals eggs for food while
the parents are away.

flavor_text_entries.sun:
It has a cunning yet savage disposition.
It waits for parents to leave their nests,
and then it sneaks in to steal their eggs.
flavor_text_entries.moon:
It uses its claws to poke holes in eggs so it can
slurp out the insides. Breeders consider it a
scourge and will drive it away or eradicate it.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-sun:
They will cooperate to steal eggs from the nests
of bird Pokémon, but fights break out to
determine which one gets to eat the eggs.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-moon:
It blends into the dark of night to ambush its
prey. Sneasel will attack Sandshrew, but its
hard skin can cause Sneasel’s claws to snap off.

flavor_text_entries.legends-arceus:
Its sturdy, curved claws are ideal for traversing precipitous cliffs.
From the tips of these claws drips a venom that infiltrates the
nerves of any prey caught in Sneasel's grasp.
